QuestData.Title: Botanist Taerix
QuestData.Description: $n, Botanist Taerix is in need of your assistance. You'll find her with her apprentices to the west, outside the ship.
QuestData.LogDescription: Speak with Botanist Taerix at the Crash Site in Ammen Vale.
QuestData.RewardText: Oh, thank goodness you've come. We have much to do.
